      <title>美国告诉盟友俄罗斯今年可能向太空发射反卫星核武器</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-20/us-tells-allies-russia-may-put-anti-satellite-nuclear-weapon-in-space-this-year</link>
