      <title>伊利诺伊州在实现三年盈余后将首次出现赤字</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-20/illinois-poised-for-first-deficit-after-three-years-of-surplus</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伊利诺伊州面临着三年来的首次预算赤字，因为该州应对从教育到移民服务等各方面成本不断上升的问题。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-20/illinois-poised-for-first-deficit-after-three-years-of-surplus</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 20 Feb 2024 18:37:45 GMT</pubDate>
