      <title>以色列与哈马斯战争导致二十国集团分裂，会议面临瘫痪风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-20/israel-hamas-war-splits-g-20-risks-paralyzing-group</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，二十国集团在加沙和乌克兰冲突问题上分歧如此之大，以至于它们今年可能被迫缩小论坛范围并完全避免地缘政治问题。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-20/israel-hamas-war-splits-g-20-risks-paralyzing-group</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 20 Feb 2024 16:41:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
